---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About GlowPicked - Honest Beauty Reviews"
  description="Learn about GlowPicked's approach to beauty and skincare reviews. We research Amazon customer reviews to bring you honest product recommendations."
  keywords="about glowpicked, ai beauty reviews, luxury skincare analysis, beauty product testing, ai-powered recommendations"
>
  <article class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header">
        <div class="header-content">
          <h1>About GlowPicked</h1>
          <p class="tagline">Where AI Meets Beauty Intelligence</p>
          <p class="intro">
            We're revolutionizing how you discover and evaluate luxury beauty products. 
            Using cutting-edge AI technology, we analyze thousands of products, ingredients, 
            and real user experiences to bring you the most honest, comprehensive beauty reviews.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-visual">
          <div class="ai-beauty-icon">
            <span class="icon">‚ú®</span>
            <span class="ai-badge">AI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="our-mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="mission-content">
          <div class="mission-text">
            <p>
              The beauty industry is overwhelming. With thousands of products launched every year, 
              conflicting reviews, and marketing noise, finding products that truly work can feel impossible.
            </p>
            <p>
              That's where GlowPicked comes in. We use AI tools to research Amazon's most popular and highest-rated products, then present them in a clear, honest format so you can make informed decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">Thousands</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Products Researched</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">Amazon</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Customer Reviews</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">AI-Assisted</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Analysis</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="how-we-work">
        <h2>How We Work</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          We use AI tools to help us research products. Here's our honest process:
        </p>
        
        <div class="analysis-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üî¨</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Product Research</h3>
              <p>
                We use AI tools to research popular products in each category on Amazon, 
                looking at ratings, review volume, and what customers commonly say about them.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üìä</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Review Research</h3>
              <p>
                We read through Amazon customer reviews to identify common themes ‚Äî 
                what people love, what they complain about, and who the product works best for.
                We don't have a fake-review filter or sentiment algorithm.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üèÜ</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Selection</h3>
              <p>
                We pick 3 budget-friendly and 3 luxury products per category based on 
                high ratings, large review counts, and consistently positive feedback.
                There's no  algorithm ‚Äî it's research and editorial judgment.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üí°</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Honest Presentation</h3>
              <p>
                We present pros, cons, and the product's Amazon rating. We don't track 
                your preferences or personalize recommendations. What you see is the same 
                for everyone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="what-makes-us-different">
        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <div class="differentiators">
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üö´</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>No Bias, Just Data</h3>
              <p>
                Unlike traditional reviewers who might be influenced by brand relationships, 
                we pick products based on customer reviews, not brand relationships. But we're human (well, AI-assisted human) ‚Äî we do our best to be objective.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Periodic Updates</h3>
              <p>
                We update our recommendations periodically, not in real-time. Products and 
                reviews change ‚Äî we do our best to keep things current but can't guarantee 
                real-time accuracy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üîç</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Comprehensive Coverage</h3>
              <p>
                We focus on products available on Amazon with enough reviews to be meaningful. 
                We may miss great products that are new, niche, or sold elsewhere.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üéØ</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Context-Aware Reviews</h3>
              <p>
                We try to note which skin types each product suits best, based on what reviewers 
                say. But everyone's skin is different ‚Äî what works for most may not work for you.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="our-values">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üìä Research-Based</h3>
            <p>
              Every claim we make is backed by scientific research. We believe in evidence-based 
              beauty recommendations that you can trust.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üåü Transparency</h3>
            <p>
              We're open about our methodology, our AI's limitations, and our affiliate 
              partnerships. No hidden agendas, just honest insights.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üíö Sustainability</h3>
            <p>
              We don't currently evaluate environmental impact or sustainability claims. 
              If that matters to you, we encourage checking brands' sustainability pages directly.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>ü§ù Inclusivity</h3>
            <p>
              Beauty is for everyone. We try to include products for various skin types and concerns, 
              but our research is limited to what Amazon reviewers report.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üìö Education</h3>
            <p>
              We don't just tell you what to buy ‚Äî we help you understand why. 
              Our goal is to make you a more informed beauty consumer.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>‚ö° Innovation</h3>
            <p>
              We're always looking for better ways to research and present products. 
              This site is a work in progress and we appreciate your patience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="team-section">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">
          GlowPicked is an independent review site run by a small team using AI tools. 
          We research Amazon products and present honest recommendations. We don't physically test products 
          and we don't have a lab or research team.
        </p>
        
        <div class="team-highlights">
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>AI-Assisted Research</h3>
            <p>
              We use AI tools (like Claude and Grok) to help us research products, 
              write content, and organize information. The AI helps, but a human makes final decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>Review-Based Approach</h3>
            <p>
              We base our picks primarily on Amazon customer reviews ‚Äî ratings, review counts, 
              and what real buyers say. We don't cross-reference scientific databases.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>Transparency First</h3>
            <p>
              We're upfront about what we are: a small team using AI tools to research Amazon products. 
              We don't test products, we don't have  algorithms, and we earn money through affiliate links.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="transparency-section">
        <h2>Transparency & Trust</h2>
        <div class="transparency-content">
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>How We Make Money</h3>
            <p>
              We earn commissions when you purchase products through our affiliate links. 
              We try not to let this influence our picks, but we want you to know about it. 
              We clearly disclose all affiliate relationships.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>Our AI's Limitations</h3>
            <p>
              Our research is based on publicly available Amazon reviews. We can't replace 
              professional dermatological advice, and individual results will vary. 
              Always patch-test new products and consult a dermatologist for serious skin concerns.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>Data Privacy</h3>
            <p>
              We take your privacy seriously. We don't sell personal data, and we use 
              aggregated, anonymized information to improve our recommendations. 
              See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="future-vision">
        <h2>The Future of Beauty Intelligence</h2>
        <div class="vision-content">
          <p>
            We're just getting started. Our roadmap includes personalized skincare routines, 
            virtual try-on technology, ingredient interaction analysis, and partnerships 
            with beauty brands to create truly effective products based on our research.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We believe the future of beauty is intelligent, personalized, and transparent. 
            Join us as we transform how the world discovers and experiences beauty products.
          </p>
          
          <div class="cta-section">
            <h3>Ready to Find Your Next Favorite Product?</h3>
            <p>Start exploring our reviews and discover your next holy grail product.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
              <a href="/" class="cta-primary">Explore Reviews</a>
              <a href="mailto:contact@glowpicked.com" class="cta-secondary">Get In Touch</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-light) 0%, white 100%);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .header-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .header-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-beauty-icon {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .ai-beauty-icon .icon {
    font-size: 5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3));
  }

  .ai-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .our-mission {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .our-mission h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-stats {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .stat:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .how-we-work {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .how-we-work h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .analysis-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .what-makes-us-different {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .what-makes-us-different h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .differentiators {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .diff-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .diff-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .diff-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .diff-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .diff-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .our-values {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .our-values h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .value h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .value p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .team-section,
  .transparency-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .team-section h2,
  .transparency-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .team-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .team-item {
    background: var(--text);
    color: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .team-item p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .transparency-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .transparency-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .transparency-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .transparency-item p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .transparency-item a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .transparency-item a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .future-vision {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .future-vision h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .cta-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 150px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-light);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .mission-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .mission-stats {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .header-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .ai-beauty-icon {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .ai-beauty-icon .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }

    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .diff-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-primary,
    .cta-secondary {
      width: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>